I have an opening for next week on the 6th I have a bunch of pre drawn pieces up for grabs. If you would like to get tattooed email me at sacredcrowtattoo@gmail.com

‼️now booking for January and February‼️ I’m now taking new clients please email me your idea, size and placement on your body. I would prefer large scale ideas but all is welcome! To book email me at sacredcrowtattoo@gmail.com

Ok Denver im finally making it out to guys in February. I’m going to be guesting with the awesome crew of @tildeathdenver if you would like to get tattooed email me at sacredcrowtattoo@gmail.com #sacred_crow
Finally finished this sleeve, tribute of my clients dog dragon. Thank you holly for the trust and dedication! It was an honor making this for you! #sacred_crow #creamtattoosupply #heritagetattoolv

So I guess it was bound to happen to me lol! I have a scammer trying to take deposits from potential clients. He’s using sacredcrowtatto@gmail.com which if you pay attention is not how you spell Tattoo. So please don’t get caught slipping! If this scammer got you please report this email thank you!

Honored to be asked by my boys @brettrosepiler wife to tattoo this super cute moth on her. I don’t usually do cute tattoos but when I do they cute! Haha! Thanks Diana! #sacred_crow #creamtattoosupply #heritagetattoolv

So for those who don’t know for the past couple of years I’ve been trying to tattoo 100 mushroom huts. As you can see from the photos I’ve tattooed 70. I have 30 to complete my endeavor and then I’m going to release a book. So if you would like to collect one please email me at sacredcrowtattoo@gmail.com once I’ve reached 100 i won’t do them again! #sacred_crow #mushroomhut

Alright folks my books are open again! I’m booking March-may I’m only booking a few months at a time to cover spending time with my family and travels. Of course I prefer large scale work but smaller one shot pieces are also welcome! #sacred_crow #heritagetattoolv

If you are interested please send us a DM, we will share all the details then. @oneblocklv
